{"id":4217,"date":"2016-12-22T15:04:31","date_gmt":"2016-12-22T23:04:31","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/?p=4217"},"modified":"2016-12-22T15:04:31","modified_gmt":"2016-12-22T23:04:31","slug":"sfis-arnie-kuhns-inducted-into-semas-mpmc-hall-of-fame","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/sfis-arnie-kuhns-inducted-into-semas-mpmc-hall-of-fame\/","title":{"rendered":"SFI&#8217;s Arnie Kuhns Inducted into SEMA&#8217;s MPMC Hall of Fame"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-4218\" src=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/MPMC-2016-HOF-Award-3-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"mpmc-2016-hof-award-3\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/MPMC-2016-HOF-Award-3-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/MPMC-2016-HOF-Award-3.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>On December 9th, 2016, SFI President and CEO Arnie Kuhns was one of three honorees inducted into SEMA&#8217;s Motorsports Parts Manufacturers Council (MPMC) Hall of Fame. During an evening reception at the Performance Racing Industry (PRI) Trade Show, the audience raised toasts to the newest inductees including our own Arnie Kuhns, Jim Hairston of PerTonix, and the legendary Smokey Yunick. The MPMC Hall of Fame recognizes those who have made a significant contribution to the MPMC or to the motorsports parts manufacturing segment as a whole.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_4219\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4219\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-4219\" src=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/MPMC-2016-HOF-Award-4-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"At the MPMC Hall of Fame Reception (L-R): Rich Barsamian, ACT (MPMC Chair), Arnie Kuhns, SFI (Inductee), Carl Olson, SFI, Jason Bruce, Holley (MPMC Chair-Elect)\" w